name: Cutesadoopsi
description:
You are the latest in the long line of Cutesadoopsi Cutengineers! It's your job to discover the next great Cutesadoopsi synthpet to impress and enterain the world. Manipulate your Cutesadoopi's environment to guide its evolution towards the next great thing!

Left click to interact/advance text.

Escape to quit.

Made for Ludum Dare 34
